{"comments":"Color algebra and semantic color tokens\n\nThis module provides:\n- Semantic color tokens (background, foreground, primary, etc.)\n- Color manipulation (lighten, darken, opacity)\n- HSL color representation\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nColors are defined semantically, not by hue. This allows themes to\nswap entire color palettes while maintaining visual hierarchy.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Style.Color as Color\n\n-- Semantic colors (map to CSS variables)\nColor.bg Color.Background      -- \"bg-background\"\nColor.bg Color.Primary         -- \"bg-primary\"\nColor.text Color.Foreground    -- \"text-foreground\"\n\n-- With opacity\nColor.bgOpacity Color.Primary 50  -- \"bg-primary/50\"\n\n-- Tailwind palette colors\nColor.bg (Color.Slate Color.C500)  -- \"bg-slate-500\"\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Color.purs","start":[141,3]},"title":"Background"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[142,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Color.purs","start":[142,3]},"title":"Foreground"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Color.purs","start":[143,3]},"title":"Card"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[144,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Color.purs","start":[144,3]},"title":"CardForeground"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[145,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Color.purs","start":[145,3]},"title":"Popover"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[146,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Color.purs","start":[146,3]},"title":"PopoverForeground"},{